	<!-- Cleric (Monolith Mechanic) Find Level 1 Toolkit Task -->

	<string id="drx_ql_pri_monolith_monolith_mechanic_stalker_task_1_name">
		<text>Retrieve Gunsmith Toolkit for Cleric</text>
	</string>
	<string id="drx_ql_pri_monolith_monolith_mechanic_stalker_task_1_text">
		<text>Retrieve the set of gunsmith tools from an infidel's stash and return them to Cleric so he can perform basic weapon and equipment upgrades.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="drx_ql_pri_monolith_monolith_mechanic_stalker_task_1_about">
		<text>An infidel has revealed the location of a set of gunsmith tools that were stashed away. You must retrieve these tools and bring them to me at once so I may upgrade the weaponry of you and your brothers. Go quickly. Do not fail.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="drx_ql_pri_monolith_monolith_mechanic_stalker_task_1_finish">
		<text>Good. You have found them.</text>
	</string>

	<!-- ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- -->
	<!-- Cleric (Monolith Mechanic) Find Level 2 Toolkit Task -->

	<string id="drx_ql_pri_monolith_monolith_mechanic_stalker_task_2_name">
		<text>Find Technician Toolkit for Cleric</text>
	</string>
	<string id="drx_ql_pri_monolith_monolith_mechanic_stalker_task_2_text">
		<text>Locate a set of technician's tools for Cleric so he can perform advanced upgrades to your equipment.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="drx_ql_pri_monolith_monolith_mechanic_stalker_task_2_about">
		<text>You must locate a set of technician's tools so that I can further upgrade the arsenal of the Monolith warriors. Search the location I have marked on your map. Do not return until you have found them. Go, now.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="drx_ql_pri_monolith_monolith_mechanic_stalker_task_2_finish">
		<text>Good. You have brought them to me.</text>
	</string>

	<!-- ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- -->
	<!-- Cleric (Monolith Mechanic) Find Level 3 Toolkit Task -->

	<string id="drx_ql_pri_monolith_monolith_mechanic_stalker_task_3_name">
		<text>Retrieve Armorer's Toolkit for Cleric</text>
	</string>
	<string id="drx_ql_pri_monolith_monolith_mechanic_stalker_task_3_text">
		<text>Kill the infidel known to be carrying a set of armorer's tools and return the tools to Cleric so he can fully upgrade your equipment.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="drx_ql_pri_monolith_monolith_mechanic_stalker_task_3_about">
		<text>There is an infidel who is known to be in possession of a set of armorer's tools. Slay the vermin and return the tools to me so that I may upgrade the weapons and equiment of the mighty Monolith warriors to it's fullest potential. Go, do not fail us.</text>
	</string>
	<string id="drx_ql_pri_monolith_monolith_mechanic_stalker_task_3_finish">
		<text>Good. You have succeeded.</text>
	</string>

